<item>
            <title>[CASSANDRA-2094] fix regression in CL.ALL read</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-2094</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;regression:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;digest message object re-used across multiple hosts.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;problem:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;shared message id, so the first digest response received will remove the callback for all others.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</description>
